st practices, please share them with us by raising a PR or [filing an issue](https://github.com/stateful/vscode-awesome-ux/issues/new).","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"## Extension Settings","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"This extension contributes the following settings:","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"* `vscode-awesome-ux.configuration.defaultNotifications`: The default value of received example notification (default `0`)","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"## Release Notes","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"See [release section](https://github.com/stateful/vscode-awesome-ux/releases).","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"---","type":"markdown"},{"editable":true,"source":"\u003cp align=\"center\"\u003e\u003csmall\u003eCopyright 2022 © \u003ca href=\"http://stateful.com/\"\u003eStateful\u003c/a\u003e – MIT License\u003c/small\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","type":"markdown"}]}
